  script\f[B]:\f[R] scripts/setup\-user.sh
.EE
.PP
Example \(en build a squashfs of the rootfs on the host:
.IP
.EX
\f[B]\-\f[R] action\f[B]:\f[R] run
  chroot\f[B]:\f[R] false
  command\f[B]:\f[R] mksquashfs ${ROOTDIR} ${ARTIFACTDIR}/root.squashfs \-comp xz \-e rwdata/
.EE
.PP
Example \(en run several commands as a single script with
\f[CR]command: |\f[R]:
.IP
.EX
